"'''Dragon Monkey'''" is the pseudonym for an individual who lettered the [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] "[[The Hovel on Terk Street]]," which was published in the [[Star Wars Tales 6|sixth issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' series by [[Dark Horse Comics]]<ref name="Hovel">{{Tales|6|The Hovel on Terk Street}}</ref> on [[December 20]], [[2000]].<ref name="date">{{DarkHorse|url=Comics/00-114/Star-Wars-Tales-6|text=Star Wars Tales #6}}</ref> Some panels of the comic were reprinted in "[[Unusual Suspects]]," an article for the ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]'' that was published in the [[Star Wars Gamer 6|sixth issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Gamer]]'' magazine by [[Wizards of the Coast]]<ref name="Gamer">{{GamerCite|6|Unusual Suspects}}</ref> on [[September 4]], [[2001]].<ref name="SW.com">{{SWArchive|url=gaming/other/rpg/news20010815.html|text=Hunting Down ''Gamer'' #6}}</ref>

